byline.contributor: Jennifer Landes contributed reporting from Cutchogue, N.Y.

abstract: Vows column on wedding of Ilze Thielmann and Aitken Thompson.
lead_paragraph: The couple married for the first time in 1995, split in 2003, became best friends, and now are newlyweds again.

headline.main: Remarrying the Ex: Ilze Thielmann and Aitken Thompson Try Again
